<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/sport-england> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Sport England (SE) helps people and communities across the country get a sporting habit for life. It also protects existing sports provision and must be consulted on any planning applications that affect playing fields in England. SE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
